OL,3,CNew proposed location for Frimley Park
OL,4,CHospital revealed
OL,6,FThe site of a golf club and woodland
OL,7,Fis the proposed new location for
OL,8,FFrimley Park Hospital, an NHS trust
OL,9,Fhas revealed.
OL,11,FFrimley Health NHS Foundation Trust
OL,12,Fannounced plans earlier this year for
OL,13,Fa #2 billion facility, with bosses
OL,14,Fsaying large parts of the current site
OL,15,Fon Portsmouth Road is built using
OL,16,Funstable RAAC (reinforced autoclaved
OL,17,Faerated concrete).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
