OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781711308
OL,3,CNew proposed location for Frimley Park
OL,4,CHospital revealed
OL,6,FThe new proposed location is part of
OL,7,Fthe land occupied by Pine Ridge Golf
OL,8,FClub, which is currently owned by
OL,9,Flocal charity Frimley Fuel Allotments.
OL,11,FThe NHS Trust says it would look to
OL,12,Facquire 55 acres of land of the 265
OL,13,Facres owned by the charity.
OL,15,FLance McCarthy, Chief Executive of
OL,16,FFrimley Health NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,17,Fsaid: "This is about creating a
OL,18,Fhospital that local people can rely on
OL,19,F- not just today, but for generations
OL,20,Fto come.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
