OL,3,CNew proposed location for Frimley Park
OL,4,CHospital revealed
OL,6,F"A new Frimley Park Hospital will mean
OL,7,Fsafer buildings, modern facilities and
OL,8,Fan environment that helps our staff
OL,9,Fdeliver the very best care."
OL,11,FUnder proposals, the new hospital
OL,12,Fwould provide emergency, inpatient and
OL,13,Fmaternity care.
OL,15,FOutpatient, diagnositc and community
OL,16,Fappointments would continue to be
OL,17,Fprovided from the current hospital
OL,18,Fsite, where the buildings are
OL,19,Funaffected by RAAC.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
