PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781711308
OL,3,CNew proposed location for Frimley Park
OL,4,CHospital revealed
OL,6,FThe trust says that this will help to
OL,7,Fkeep travel disruption to a minimum
OL,8,Fand reduce pressure on local roads.
OL,10,FFrimley Health has not purchased the
OL,11,Fland and says no final decisions have
OL,12,Fbeen made.
OL,14,FIt would need the approval of the
OL,15,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,16,Fbefore any land was bought.
OL,18,FA planning application for the new
OL,19,Fhospital is planned to be submitted in
OL,20,Fautumn 2027.
